# PANTONE SkinTone Guide

![Pantone SkinTone Guide](https://www.pantone.com/media/wysiwyg/pages/skintone/pantone-skintone-guide-limited-edition-stg203-product-1.jpg?auto=webp&format=pjpg&quality=85)

The newly expanded 2023 SkinTone™ Guide includes 28 new shades in addition to the 110 existing SkinTone™ Guide shades. These 28 new shades consist of a wider array of darker tones and yellow undertones, an expansion inspired and informed by Pantone® customers seeking out specific color matches that represent their communities.

Available for the first time in a Limited-Edition Cover version, the Pantone® SkinTone™ Guide has helped customers across fashion and beauty industries, as well as customers involved in product design, represent diverse and inclusive skin tones for the last decade.

View the SkinTone Guide

