## Digital Gaming

Pantone® SkinTone™ Validated to ensure that display, TV, mobile device, and printer manufacturers are able to accurately produce realistic skin tones when creating video game avatars, allowing players to create an even more immersive experience.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Toys

The SkinTone™ Guide is a great reference which designers can use when creating toy color pallets to make them as inclusive as possible. Toys with a diverse range of skin tones can empower children to be proud of their identity and celebrate the beauty of their own skin color.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Prothestics

The Pantone® SkinTone™ Guide helps prosthetic designers create healthcare products that match the exact skin tone of their patients, with the help of laser scanning and Pantone®'s color matching system.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Apparel

The SkinTone™ Guide provides a tool for those in the apparel industry to discover complementary colors to use in their collections that look good on a variety of skin tones. It can help speed up the development process and create more inclusive ranges.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Intimates

The Pantone® SkinTone™ Guide is a useful tool for intimate apparel companies to accurately match skin tones for their customers. It provides a wide range of real skin tones as reference points, ensuring their lines are inclusive for all.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Cosmetics

The SkinTone™ Guide provides a comprehensive range of warm, cool, and neutral tones in deeper and lighter shades to help customers find their perfect match in cosmetics. It can also be used to assess which shades of complimentary colors are most suitable for different skin tones.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Skincare

Skincare companies are working to make their products more inclusive to a global customer base with SkinTone™ Guide, which provides a reference for 138 different skin tones. This helps ensure that the same formula looks different on different skin tones and blends in accordingly.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

## Costume Design

The Pantone SkinTone™ Guide helps designers find the right colors for costumes and props that match the skin tones of actors. The Guide is intended to be used together with the Pantone Fashion Home & Interiors Guide to create coordinated color schemes that help bring a production to life.

[Learn More >](https://www.pantone.com/articles/product-spotlight/introducing-the-2023-pantone-skintone-guide/ "Click to View Pantone SkinTone Guide")

