Celebrating 10 Years of Self-Expression Through Color with 138 Dynamic Shades

The 2023 SkinTone™ Guide is dedicated to Pantone’s® continuous, ongoing effort to try to include every skin tone match imaginable and undertake the rigorous backend work to ensure this guide is reflective of true coloring across a wider array of skin colors. Our goal is to provide an inclusive, global product, in both digital (Pantone® Connect) and physical spaces, that reflects a global society and empower companies to offer more inclusive color matches for their audiences around the world.

